This morning I had to explain to a man in his 20's about composting.  That uncooked fruit / veg. goes in the tray to go into the compost.  Isnt' this standard in every house? #SchoolsStrike4Climate

I've rented rooms to many 20somethings in the past number of years.  I've had to explain recycling, composting and energy efficiency to them.  There must be no peer pressure in these areas #Striking4Climate
